[
  {
    "content_id": 340892,
    "reference_id": 13578,
    "title": "約翰三書1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>這封信的作者是作長老的約翰：譯者們已添加<em>約翰</em>的詞條（見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"13591\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">研讀註釋約貳1:1</span>）。</p></li><li><p>新約中有幾個名叫該猶的人（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:29\">徒19:29</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:4\">20:4；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:23\">羅16:23；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:14\">林前1:14</a>）；該猶這個名字在希臘羅馬世界很常見。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:1",
          "end_ref": "64001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 13591,
          "content_id": 694141,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "約翰二書 1:1",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340885,
    "reference_id": 13571,
    "title": "約翰三書1:1–4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001001-64001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約翰的這封書信以傳統的問候開篇，包括了指明作者和收信人、問候（親愛的<em>兄弟</em>〔dear friend〕）、為收信人祝福，以及為他們情誼的某方面感恩。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:1",
          "end_ref": "64001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340893,
    "reference_id": 13579,
    "title": "約翰三書1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>弟兄（有些譯本譯為「旅行教師（the traveling teachers）」）可能是約翰差派的使者，他們從一間教會到另一間教會，傳講福音並鼓勵信徒（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:5\">1:5</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:10\">10</a>）。</p></li><li><p>你按真理而行：該猶忠於使徒所傳講的耶穌基督的福音。假教師否認耶穌基督道成肉身並為贖罪而犧牲的事實（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1-1John4:3\">約壹4:1–3</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:3",
          "end_ref": "64001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340894,
    "reference_id": 13580,
    "title": "約翰三書1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span>跟《約翰二書》一樣</span>（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:1-2John1:4\">約二1:1–4</a>），約翰（在這裡）強調的是認識真理並按真理而行，這與丟特腓及其追隨者形成了對比（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:9\">約三1:9</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:4",
          "end_ref": "64001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340896,
    "reference_id": 13582,
    "title": "約翰三書1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約翰差派旅行教師們（和合本譯為<em>「作客旅之弟兄」，</em>更符合原希臘文字面意思）從一間教會到另一間教會，在使徒所傳講的基督教導上堅固眾人，該猶接待了（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:7-3John1:8\">1:7–8</a>）這些教師。通過這樣的接待，該猶表明他已經領受了使徒所教導的真理，因此他在神面前是忠心的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:5",
          "end_ref": "64001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340895,
    "reference_id": 13581,
    "title": "約翰三書1:5–8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001005-64001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>約翰現在鼓勵該猶繼續支持自己所差派的旅行教師（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:3\">1:3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:5",
          "end_ref": "64001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340897,
    "reference_id": 13583,
    "title": "約翰三書1:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這裡所說的教會很可能位於以弗所，約翰當時可能就住在以弗所。以弗所是亞細亞省的重要港口城市，是羅馬帝國的第四大城市。它成為基督徒社群的重要城市（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:19-Acts19:41\">徒18:19–19:41；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3\">提前1:3；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:1\">彼前1:1；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:1-Rev2:7\">啟2:1–7</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:6",
          "end_ref": "64001006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340898,
    "reference_id": 13584,
    "title": "約翰三書1:7–8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001007-64001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>「為主的名」：約翰不需要說明這是誰的名，因為早期的所有基督徒都知道<em>這名</em>代表了耶穌基督（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:41\">徒5:41</a>）。</p></li><li><p>這些旅行教師選擇不接受非基督徒的供給<em>，</em>而是完全依靠教會的支持。為獲得認可的旅行教師提供支持的基督徒，就在這些教師教導真理的事工上成為他們的同工（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:41-Matt10:42\">太10:41–42</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:15-Phil4:19\">腓4:15–19</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:7",
          "end_ref": "64001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340900,
    "reference_id": 13586,
    "title": "約翰三書1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>我曾略略地寫信給教會：這可能是指《約翰一書》或一封現已遺失了的信。</p></li><li><p>丟特腓驕傲自大（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:6\">提前3:6</a>），受自私野心的驅使。</p></li><li><p>拒絕與我們有任何關係（和合本譯為「不接待我們」）：約翰在《約翰一書》中處理的一個重要問題就是這樣的異議（見，例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:19\">約壹2:19，</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:5-1John4:6\">4:5–6</a>）。丟特腓拒絕接待約翰派去的教師，並將接待這些教師的教會成員逐出教會。他想要統治地方教會，並且拒絕任何外部權柄的督責。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:9",
          "end_ref": "64001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340899,
    "reference_id": 13585,
    "title": "約翰三書1:9–12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001009-64001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在這段經文中，約翰譴責丟特腓，並稱讚底米丟為按真理而活之忠心基督徒的榜樣。約翰勸勉該猶效法底米丟。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:9",
          "end_ref": "64001012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340886,
    "reference_id": 13572,
    "title": "約翰三書1:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>行惡的：丟特腓未能遵循基督徒彼此相愛的原則，因而受到了譴責（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10-1John3:14\">約一3:10–14</a>）。該猶可以據此確認丟特腓並沒有在按真理而活。這可以應用於拒絕使徒與耶穌基督相關的教導，並拒絕與領受使徒教導之人團契相交的所有人身上。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:11",
          "end_ref": "64001011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340887,
    "reference_id": 13573,
    "title": "約翰三書1:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>底米丟與丟特腓截然不同，他是一個認識真理並按真理而行的典範（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:3\">1:3</a>）。底米丟的名字出現在信的末尾，這暗示他就是把約翰的信帶給該猶之人（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:7-Col4:9\">西4:7–9；</a><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:12\">彼前5:12</a>）。</p></li><li><p>你也知道我們的見證是真的：約翰想要保護在這些教會中他作為值得信賴之長老的名譽，而不想因丟特腓和其他假教師可能的篡權蒙羞辱。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:12",
          "end_ref": "64001012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340889,
    "reference_id": 13575,
    "title": "約翰三書1:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>筆墨（字面意思是<em>墨和蘆葦</em>）：在古代，書寫通常用的是由蘆葦製成的筆和黑色碳墨（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:12\">約貳1:12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:13",
          "end_ref": "64001013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340888,
    "reference_id": 13574,
    "title": "約翰三書1:13–15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001013-64001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>與《約翰二書》一樣，在《約翰三書》的結尾約翰表達了希望親自探訪並落實這封信中的指示。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:13",
          "end_ref": "64001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340890,
    "reference_id": 13576,
    "title": "約翰三書1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>「當面」：英文中面對面（face to face）這個慣用語與這裡使用的希臘文慣用語相似，希臘文字面意思是<em>口對口（mouth to mouth）；</em> 另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:12\">約貳1:12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:14",
          "end_ref": "64001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 340891,
    "reference_id": 13577,
    "title": "約翰三書1:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "64001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>約翰用告別和致敬結束了他的這封信。</p></li><li><p>問你平安：這是猶太人之間的傳統問候（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:12\">太10:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:5-Luke10:6\">路10:5–6</a>），對基督徒來說它具有更深刻的含義，因為耶穌在復活後說了這句話（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:19-John20:21\">約20:19–21</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:26\">26</a>）。</p></li><li><p>請你替我按著姓名問眾位朋友安：該猶要問候眾位朋友——也就是那些接受使徒所講的福音並按真理而活之人（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:3-3John1:4\">約三1:3–4</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "64001015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:15",
          "end_ref": "64001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "3JN 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  }
